fdaDrugLabel.indication: INDICATIONS: For temporary relief of painful lower back with burning, looseness of ligaments and general soreness, aching tendons, ligaments, and bones.

nciThesaurus.definition: A nutritional supplement gleaned from the exoskeleton of the shark. Shark cartilage inhibits metalloproteinases (MMPs) and possesses antiangiogenic and antimetastatic properties.
